title: EXPLORING THE NATURAL SPLENDOR – ECO TOUR IN KORAPUT WITH DESIA KORAPUT
text:
Embarking on an eco tour allows us to reconnect with nature, appreciate its beauty, and contribute to its preservation. In the enchanting land of Koraput, nestled in the eastern state of Odisha, India, lies a treasure trove of biodiversity and cultural heritage waiting to be discovered. Join Desia Koraput, the leading eco-tourism agency in Koraput, as we delve into the mesmerizing landscapes and cultural richness of Koraput, ensuring an unforgettable eco tour experience.During your eco tour in Koraput, explore the famous Duduma Waterfalls, towering at 157 meters, and witness the, mesmerizing sight of water cascading down the rocks. With Desia Koraput, you can embark on guided nature walks, bird watching expeditions and wildlife safaris, enabling you to fully appreciate the region’s ecological marvels.
